544
00:37:37,340 --> 00:37:38,890
Do I look like a Genius Bar to you?

545
00:37:39,540 --> 00:37:41,770
I'm sorry. I'm sitting here
defending the free world

546
00:37:41,860 --> 00:37:43,610
